Originally made by cayden. Modified by Charamellized.
The basic resolution is: 2732x1536 (it can be lower) The import button is the image which is going to be imported as the osu! background. The reset button is going to delete the image you imported and can fix some problems. Make sure when you click on reset, launch osu! and cycle through songs for around 20 times to load all the background. The convert button is used for converting png to jpg. To make it work, put seasonal background as always.
This program was modified to not use a paid library, which is the reason why it was not working.
